}}'''宝玑'''（{{lang-en|Breguet}}），是奢华钟表及珠宝品牌、製造商，1775年由[[亚伯拉罕·路易·宝玑|亚伯拉罕·路易·宝玑]]在[[法国|法国]][[巴黎|巴黎]]创立，现总部位于[[瑞士|瑞士]][[拉拜|拉拜]]。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.breguet.com/en/history|title=History {{!}} Breguet|accessdate=2018-12-20|work=www.breguet.com|archive-date=2021-02-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210212092229/https://www.breguet.com/en/history|dead-url=no}}</ref> 宝玑是世界上最古老的钟表品牌之一，1999年成为瑞士[[斯沃琪集团|斯沃琪集团]]（Swatch）的子公司。<ref name=":4" /> 宝玑也是众多制表技术的开拓者，亚伯拉罕·路易·宝玑于1780年发明并制造了世界上第一款[[自动机械表|自动机械表]]（the ''Perpétuelle''）、于1801年发明并制造出了[[陀飛輪|陀飞轮]]、于1810年发明并制造出了世界上第一款[[腕錶|腕表]]（宝玑No. 2639，[[那不勒斯|那不勒斯]]王后[[卡罗琳·波拿巴|卡罗琳·波拿巴]]订制）。<ref name=":7">{{Cite web|url=https://www.breguet.com/en/history/inventions|title=Inventions {{!}} Breguet|accessdate=2018-12-20|work=www.breguet.com|archive-date=2021-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210104012855/https://www.breguet.com/en/history/inventions|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":15">{{Cite web|url=https://museum.seiko.co.jp/en/knowledge/episode/episode_03/|title=Abraham-Louis Breguet {{!}} Timepiece Luminaries {{!}} THE SEIKO MUSEUM|website=museum.seiko.co.jp|access-date=2019-01-06|archive-date=2019-01-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190106153321/https://museum.seiko.co.jp/en/knowledge/episode/episode_03/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":16">{{Cite web|url=https://www.breguet.com/en/history/inventions/self-winding|title=Self-winding {{!}} Breguet|website=www.breguet.com|access-date=2019-01-06|archive-date=2020-11-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124235953/https://www.breguet.com/en/history/inventions/self-winding|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="HISTOIRE">[http://www.tendancehorlogerie.com/histoire-de-la-maison-breguet/ "Histoire de la Maison Breguet"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.tendancehorlogerie.com/histoire-de-la-maison-breguet/ |date=20110513095232 }}, ''Tendance Horologie'', 16 April 2009 (French)</ref><ref name=":14">{{Cite web|url=https://www.breguet.com/en/history/inventions/first-wris