=== 玛丽·安托瓦内特怀表 ===
宝玑第160号（Breguet No. 160），也被称为[[玛丽·安托瓦内特|玛丽·安托瓦内特]]怀表（Marie-Antoinette pocket watch )。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":3" /> 1783年，法国王后玛丽·安托瓦内特的爱慕者瑞典[[伯爵|伯爵]]Axel Von Fersen向宝玑订购一枚怀表，作为赠予王后的礼物。<ref name=":02">{{Cite web|url=https://www.breguet.com/zh-hant/%E5%AF%B6%E7%92%A3%E4%B9%8B%E5%AE%B6/%E8%A3%BD%E8%A1%A8%E5%BB%A0/%E7%91%AA%E9%BA%97%E2%80%A2%E5%AE%89%E6%89%98%E7%93%A6%E5%85%A7%E7%89%B9%E6%87%B7%E8%A1%A8|title=「Grande Complication」編號1160懷表|website=www.breguet.com|access-date=2018-12-14|accessdate=|author=|date=|publisher=|archive-date=2020-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113022309/https://www.breguet.com/zh-hant/%E5%AF%B6%E7%92%A3%E4%B9%8B%E5%AE%B6/%E8%A3%BD%E8%A1%A8%E5%BB%A0/%E7%91%AA%E9%BA%97%E2%80%A2%E5%AE%89%E6%89%98%E7%93%A6%E5%85%A7%E7%89%B9%E6%87%B7%E8%A1%A8|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":32">{{Cite web|url=https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/breguet-number-1160-marie-antoinette-replica|title=Hands-On: The Breguet Number 1160, A Replica Of The Famous Watch Made For Marie Antoinette|last=April 21|first=Arthur Touchot|language=en|last2=2017|website=HODINKEE|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111183132/https://www.hodinkee.com/articles/breguet-number-1160-marie-antoinette-replica|dead-url=no}}</ref> 订制要求怀表“越卓越越好，需要汇集当时所有已知的复杂制表工艺”。<ref name=":02" /><ref name=":12">{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/aliciaadamczyk/2014/10/14/breguet-marie-antoinette-watch/|title=Return of the Queen: The Curious Saga of Breguet's Infamous Marie Antoinette Watch|last=Adamczyk|first=Alicia|language=en|website=Forbes|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2021-01-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210117191111/https://www.forbes.com/sites/aliciaadamczyk/2014/10/14/breguet-marie-antoinette-watch/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 订单没有时间限制、没有金额上限。<ref name=":02" />

最终的成品就是宝玑第160号超级复杂怀表。成品最终于1827年完工，但是玛丽·安托瓦内特王后已经去世34年（在[[法国大革命|法国大革命]]中被斩首）、宝玑先生本人也已经去世4年（成品最终由宝玑先生的儿子制作完成）。<ref name=":02" /><ref name=":12" /> 该怀表总共耗时44年才制造完成。<ref name=":02" /><ref name=":12" />

该怀表先前一直保存在[[以色列|以色列]][[耶路撒冷|耶路撒冷]]的伊斯兰艺术博物馆（The Museum for Islamic Art ），但1983年被盗窃。<ref name=":02" /><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=https://robbreport.com/style/watch-collector/breguet-got-away-historys-greatest-watch-heist-230103/|title=The Breguet That Got Away: History’s Greatest Watch Heist|date=2015-12-02|last=Bell|first=Rebekah|language=en|website=Robb Report|access-date=2018-12-14|archive-date=2020-11-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201108195619/https://robbreport.com/style/watch-collector/breguet-got-away-historys-greatest-watch-heist-230103/|dead-url=no}}</ref> 直到2007年，该怀表才被找回并归还博物馆。<ref name=":02" /><ref name=":2" />

